{"chapter_number":78,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":80,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"النبإ","name_complex":"An-Naba","name_simple":"An-Naba","verses_count":40,"pages":[582,583],"meaning":{"text":"The Tidings","en":"The Tidings","id":"Berita Besar"},"verses":[[[1,5673,"78:1","عَمَّ يَتَسَاءَلُونَ",["Of what do they ask one another?","Tentang apakah mereka saling bertanya-tanya?"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[2,5674,"78:2","عَنِ النَّبَإِ الْعَظِيمِ",["About the great event,","Tentang berita yang besar (hari kebangkitan),"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[3,5675,"78:3","الَّذِي هُمْ فِيهِ مُخْتَلِفُونَ",["About which they differ?","yang dalam hal itu mereka berselisih."],582,30,59,233,null,null],[4,5676,"78:4","كَلَّا سَيَعْلَمُونَ",["Nay! they shall soon come to know","Tidak! Kelak mereka akan mengetahui,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[5,5677,"78:5","ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَيَعْلَمُونَ",["Nay! Nay! they shall soon know.","sekali lagi tidak! Kelak mereka akan mengetahui."],582,30,59,233,null,null],[6,5678,"78:6","أَلَمْ نَجْعَلِ الْأَرْضَ مِهَادًا",["Have We not made the earth an even expanse?","Bukankah Kami telah menjadikan bumi sebagai hamparan,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[7,5679,"78:7","وَالْجِبَالَ أَوْتَادًا",["And the mountains as projections (thereon)?","dan gunung-gunung sebagai pasak?"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[8,5680,"78:8","وَخَلَقْنَاكُمْ أَزْوَاجًا",["And We created you in pairs,","Dan Kami menciptakan kamu berpasang-pasangan,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[9,5681,"78:9","وَجَعَلْنَا نَوْمَكُمْ سُبَاتًا",["And We made your sleep to be rest (to you),","dan Kami menjadikan tidurmu untuk istirahat,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[10,5682,"78:10","وَجَعَلْنَا اللَّيْلَ لِبَاسًا",["And We made the night to be a covering,","dan Kami menjadikan malam sebagai pakaian"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[11,5683,"78:11","وَجَعَلْنَا النَّهَارَ مَعَاشًا",["And We made the day for seeking livelihood.","dan Kami menjadikan siang untuk mencari penghidupan,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[12,5684,"78:12","وَبَنَيْنَا فَوْقَكُمْ سَبْعًا شِدَادًا",["And We made above you seven strong ones,","dan Kami membangun di atas kamu tujuh (langit) yang kokoh,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[13,5685,"78:13","وَجَعَلْنَا سِرَاجًا وَهَّاجًا",["And We made a shining lamp,","dan Kami menjadikan pelita yang terang-benderang (matahari),"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[14,5686,"78:14","وَأَنزَلْنَا مِنَ الْمُعْصِرَاتِ مَاءً ثَجَّاجًا",["And We send down from the clouds water pouring forth abundantly,","dan Kami turunkan dari awan, air hujan yang tercurah dengan hebatnya,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[15,5687,"78:15","لِّنُخْرِجَ بِهِ حَبًّا وَنَبَاتًا",["That We may bring forth thereby corn and herbs,","untuk Kami tumbuhkan dengan air itu biji-bijian dan tanam-tanaman,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[16,5688,"78:16","وَجَنَّاتٍ أَلْفَافًا",["And gardens dense and luxuriant.","dan kebun-kebun yang rindang."],582,30,59,233,null,null],[17,5689,"78:17","إِنَّ يَوْمَ الْفَصْلِ كَانَ مِيقَاتًا",["Surely the day of decision is (a day) appointed:","Sungguh, hari keputusan adalah suatu waktu yang telah ditetapkan,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[18,5690,"78:18","يَوْمَ يُنفَخُ فِي الصُّورِ فَتَأْتُونَ أَفْوَاجًا",["The day on which the trumpet shall be blown so you shall come forth in hosts,","(yaitu) pada hari (ketika) sangkakala ditiup, lalu kamu datang berbondong-bondong,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[19,5691,"78:19","وَفُتِحَتِ السَّمَاءُ فَكَانَتْ أَبْوَابًا",["And the heaven shall be opened so that it shall be all openings,","dan langit pun dibukalah, maka terdapatlah beberapa pintu,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[20,5692,"78:20","وَسُيِّرَتِ الْجِبَالُ فَكَانَتْ سَرَابًا",["And the mountains shall be moved off so that they shall remain a mere semblance.","dan gunung-gunung pun dijalankan sehingga menjadi fatamorgana."],582,30,59,233,null,null],[21,5693,"78:21","إِنَّ جَهَنَّمَ كَانَتْ مِرْصَادًا",["Surely hell lies in wait,","Sungguh, (neraka) Jahanam itu (sebagai) tempat mengintai (bagi penjaga yang mengawasi isi neraka),"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[22,5694,"78:22","لِّلطَّاغِينَ مَآبًا",["A place of resort for the inordinate,","menjadi tempat kembali bagi orang-orang yang melampaui batas."],582,30,59,233,null,null],[23,5695,"78:23","لَّابِثِينَ فِيهَا أَحْقَابًا",["Living therein for ages.","Mereka tinggal di sana dalam masa yang lama,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[24,5696,"78:24","لَّا يَذُوقُونَ فِيهَا بَرْدًا وَلَا شَرَابًا",["They shall not taste therein cool nor drink","mereka tidak merasakan kesejukan di dalamnya dan tidak (pula mendapat) minuman,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[25,5697,"78:25","إِلَّا حَمِيمًا وَغَسَّاقًا",["But boiling and intensely cold water,","selain air yang mendidih dan nanah,"],582,30,59,233,null,null],[26,5698,"78:26","جَزَاءً وِفَاقًا",["Requital corresponding.","sebagai pembalasan yang setimpal."],582,30,59,233,null,null],[27,5699,"78:27","إِنَّهُمْ كَانُوا لَا يَرْجُونَ حِسَابًا",["Surely they feared not the account,","Sesungguhnya dahulu mereka tidak pernah mengharapkan perhitungan."],582,30,59,233,null,null],[28,5700,"78:28","وَكَذَّبُوا بِآيَاتِنَا كِذَّابًا",["And called Our communications a lie, giving the lie (to the truth).","Dan mereka benar-benar mendustakan ayat-ayat Kami."],582,30,59,233,null,null],[29,5701,"78:29","وَكُلَّ شَيْءٍ أَحْصَيْنَاهُ كِتَابًا",["And We have recorded everything in a book,","Dan segala sesuatu telah Kami catat dalam suatu Kitab (buku catatan amalan manusia)."],582,30,59,233,null,null],[30,5702,"78:30","فَذُوقُوا فَلَن نَّزِيدَكُمْ إِلَّا عَذَابًا",["So taste! for We will not add to you aught but chastisement.","Maka karena itu rasakanlah! Maka tidak ada yang akan Kami tambahkan kepadamu selain azab."],582,30,59,233,null,null],[31,5703,"78:31","إِنَّ لِلْمُتَّقِينَ مَفَازًا",["Surely for those who guard (against evil) is achievement,","Sungguh, orang-orang yang bertakwa mendapat kemenangan,"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[32,5704,"78:32","حَدَائِقَ وَأَعْنَابًا",["Gardens and vineyards,","(yaitu) kebun-kebun dan buah anggur,"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[33,5705,"78:33","وَكَوَاعِبَ أَتْرَابًا",["And voluptuous women of equal age;","dan gadis-gadis montok yang sebaya,"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[34,5706,"78:34","وَكَأْسًا دِهَاقًا",["And a pure cup.","dan gelas-gelas yang penuh (berisi minuman)."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[35,5707,"78:35","لَّا يَسْمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغْوًا وَلَا كِذَّابًا",["They shall not hear therein any vain words nor lying.","Di sana mereka tidak mendengar percakapan yang sia-sia maupun (perkataan) dusta."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[36,5708,"78:36","جَزَاءً مِّن رَّبِّكَ عَطَاءً حِسَابًا",["A reward from your Lord, a gift according to a reckoning:","Sebagai balasan dan pemberian yang cukup banyak dari Tuhanmu,"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[37,5709,"78:37","رَّبِّ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ وَمَا بَيْنَهُمَا الرَّحْمَٰنِ ۖ لَا يَمْلِكُونَ مِنْهُ خِطَابًا",["The Lord of the heavens and the earth and what is between them, the Beneficent Allah, they shall not be able to address Him.","Tuhan (yang memelihara) langit dan bumi dan apa yang ada di antara keduanya; Yang Maha Pengasih, mereka tidak mampu berbicara dengan Dia."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[38,5710,"78:38","يَوْمَ يَقُومُ الرُّوحُ وَالْمَلَائِكَةُ صَفًّا ۖ لَّا يَتَكَلَّمُونَ إِلَّا مَنْ أَذِنَ لَهُ الرَّحْمَٰنُ وَقَالَ صَوَابًا",["The day on which the spirit and the angels shall stand in ranks; they shall not speak except he whom the Beneficent Allah permits and who speaks the right thing.","Pada hari, ketika ruh dan para malaikat berdiri bersaf-saf, mereka tidak berkata-kata, kecuali siapa yang telah diberi izin kepadanya oleh Tuhan Yang Maha Pengasih dan dia hanya mengatakan yang benar."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[39,5711,"78:39","ذَٰلِكَ الْيَوْمُ الْحَقُّ ۖ فَمَن شَاءَ اتَّخَذَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّهِ مَآبًا",["That is the sure day, so whoever desires may take refuge with his Lord.","Itulah hari yang pasti terjadi. Maka barang siapa menghendaki, niscaya dia menempuh jalan kembali kepada Tuhannya."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[40,5712,"78:40","إِنَّا أَنذَرْنَاكُمْ عَذَابًا قَرِيبًا يَوْمَ يَنظُرُ الْمَرْءُ مَا قَدَّمَتْ يَدَاهُ وَيَقُولُ الْكَافِرُ يَا لَيْتَنِي كُنتُ تُرَابًا",["Surely We have warned you of a chastisement near at hand: the day when man shall see what his two hands have sent before, and the unbeliever shall say: O! would that I were dust!","Sesungguhnya Kami telah memperingatkan kepadamu (orang kafir) azab yang dekat, pada hari manusia melihat apa yang telah diperbuat oleh kedua tangannya; dan orang kafir berkata, “Alangkah baiknya seandainya dahulu aku jadi tanah.”"],583,30,59,233,null,null]],[[[1,3,582,"&#xfb51;","word","عَمَّ",["About what",""]],[2,3,582,"&#xfb52;","word","يَتَسَاءَلُونَ",["are they asking one another",""]],[3,3,582,"&#xfb53;","end","ﭓ",[null,null]]],[[1,3,582,"&#xfb54;","word","عَنِ",["About","dari/tentang"]],[2,3,582,"&#xfb55;","word","النَّبَإِ",["the News","berita"]],[3,3,582,"&#xfb56;","word","الْعَظِيمِ",["the Great","besar"]],[4,3,582,"&#xfb57;","end","ﭗ",[null,null]]],[[1,3,582,"&#xfb58;","word","الَّذِي",["(About) which","yang"]],[2,3,582,"&#xfb59;","word","هُمْ",["they","mereka"]],[3,3,582,"&#xfb5a;","word","فِيهِ",["(are) concerning it","di dalamnya/tentang itu"]],[4,3,582,"&#xfb5b;","word","مُخْتَلِفُونَ",["(in) disagreement","orang yang berselisih"]],[5,3,582,"&#xfb5c;","end","ﭜ",[null,null]]],[[1,4,582,"&#xfb5d;","word","كَلَّا",["Nay","jangan begitu/sekali-kali tidak"]],[2,4,582,"&#xfb5e;","word","سَيَعْلَمُونَ",["(soon) they will know","kelak mereka akan mengetahui"]],[3,4,582,"&#xfb5f;","end","ﭟ",[null,null]]],[[1,4,582,"&#xfb60;","word","ثُمَّ",["Then","kemudian"]],[2,4,582,"&#xfb61;","word","كَلَّا",["Nay","jangan begitu/sekali-kali tidak"]],[3,4,582,"&#xfb62;","word","سَيَعْلَمُونَ",["(soon) they will know","kelak mereka akan mengetahui"]],[4,4,582,"&#xfb63;","end","ﭣ",[null,null]]],[[1,4,582,"&#xfb64;","word","أَلَمْ",["Have not","tidaklah/bukanlah"]],[2,4,582,"&#xfb65;","word","نَجْعَلِ",["We